ww.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/milei-in-israel-argentine-president-goes-on-a-personal-journey-at-a-time-of-unrest/0000018d-a76c-d9a5-afdd-b76d1ed50000</guid></item><item><title>名人签署公开信支持以色列参加欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</link><description>包括知名犹太名人在内的数百名娱乐业资深人士支持欧洲广播联盟将以色列纳入今年欧洲电视网比赛的承诺，尽管在加沙持续战争中要求将以色列排除在外的呼声很高</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 15:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/celebrities-sign-open-letter-in-support-of-israeli-inclusion-in-eurovision-contest/0000018d-a7db-dc85-a9af-bfff5a830000</guid></item><item><title>五年后，耗资 3000 万谢克尔，东耶路撒冷缆车项目仍滞留在半空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</link><description>尽管该州一年多来一直在努力寻找一家国际公司来建设缆车网络，但西尔万的巴勒斯坦居民的土地仍然被征用，橄榄树也被连根拔起</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 14:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/five-years-and-30-million-shekels-later-east-jerusalem-cable-car-project-is-stuck-midair/0000018d-a79e-d9a5-afdd-b7dfe5f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党的威慑平衡取决于哈马斯在开罗的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉再次表示，尽管以色列努力将黎巴嫩问题单独对待，但只有在加沙达成停火后，才会在北部边境达成协议。球在以色列这边，但以色列对真主党的要求不仅仅是停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</guid></item><item><title>SUV 盗窃浪潮引发人们对来自约旦河西岸的另一场 10 月 7 日式袭击的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</link><description>过去几周，以色列发生了铃木吉姆尼盗窃案。许多人再次出现在约旦河西岸，导致一些人担心这些盗窃行为是袭击计划的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹，导致一名以色列人死亡、八人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</link><description>炮火攻击的目标是以色列北部城市萨法德的一个军事基地；以色列国防军表示正在回应并打击黎巴嫩的火源</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属前往国际法庭敦促起诉哈马斯领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</link><description>以色列不是国际刑事法院成员，也不承认其管辖权，但检察官卡里姆·汗本周重申，该法院对 10 月 7 日事件拥有管辖权。人质家属代表团希望法院逮捕哈马斯领导人认股权证</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</guid></item><item><title>“严重关切”：犹太领导人致信以色列外长，谴责部长们与瑞典极右翼政党的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</link><description>在给以色列外交部长的一封信中，欧洲犹太人大会和瑞典犹太社区理事会的领导人警告不要与瑞典民主党结盟，信中称瑞典民主党“自称是我们的盟友”，同时主张“犹太人不能是瑞典人” .&amp;#39;该党根源于新纳粹和反犹太主义意识形态</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空表示，由于战时低成本航站楼关闭，该公司取消了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</link><description>瑞安航空在 10 月 7 日取消飞往以色列的航班后仅两周前就续签了部分航线。这家总部位于都柏林的航空公司在周二发布的一份声明中表示，“期待在低成本航站楼 1 号航站楼重新开放后恢复运营”。打开&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列担心更多西方国家会效仿制裁暴力的西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-additional-western-countries-will-follow-suit-in-sanctioning-violent-settlers/0000018d-a6a3-d9a5-afdd-b7eff18b0000</link><description>法国效仿美国和英国，选择不等待欧盟的决定。一位以色列高级政治人物表示，如果政府不对暴力定居者执行法律，这可能会为制裁以色列士兵和领导人打开大门</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 09:59:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-additional-western-countries-will-follow-suit-in-sanctioning-violent-settlers/0000018d-a6a3-d9a5-afdd-b7eff18b0000</guid></item><item><title>议会小组将权衡针对个人表达的极右翼反煽动法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-to-weigh-tougher-anti-incitement-laws-targeting-individual-expressions/0000018d-a403-d8e9-a3bf-f7234e9a0000</link><description>民间社会团体和公设辩护人办公室反对这些法案，认为这些法案没有必要且反民主。民权倡导者警告说，这可能相当于思想警务</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 04:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-to-weigh-tougher-anti-incitement-laws-targeting-individual-expressions/0000018d-a403-d8e9-a3bf-f7234e9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团参加开罗人质谈判的余地有限——内塔尼亚胡并不急于达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-sent-its-delegation-to-cairo-but-a-hostage-deal-is-not-their-top-priority/0000018d-a424-d400-a7cd-ffa7bd490000</link><description>总理继续坚称，军事压力最终将导致以色列达成一项条件更好的协议，无视人质家属的抗议。看来新的人质协议并不是以色列代表团的首要任务</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-sent-its-delegation-to-cairo-but-a-hostage-deal-is-not-their-top-priority/0000018d-a424-d400-a7cd-ffa7bd490000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属抨击内塔尼亚胡不参加开罗哈马斯会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-live/idf-publishes-footage-of-hamas-leader-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel-from-beginning-of-war/0000018d-a582-d9a5-afdd-b7cf8e490000</link><description>以色列空军在黎巴嫩发动大规模空袭，造成一名以色列人死亡、八人受伤 ■ 土耳其总统埃尔多安抵达开罗，这是自 2012 年以来的首次正式访问 ■ 世卫组织警告以色列对拉法的袭击将是一场“深不可测的灾难” ■ 报告：人质谈判开罗延期 ■ 加沙人质家属代表团前往海牙国际刑事法院</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 02:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article-live/idf-publishes-footage-of-hamas-leader-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel-from-beginning-of-war/0000018d-a582-d9a5-afdd-b7cf8e490000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大总理谴责针对多伦多犹太医院的抗议活动“应受谴责”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/canadian-pm-denounces-reprehensible-protest-targeting-jewish-hospital-in-toronto/0000018d-a4f0-d42f-adcd-eff07cff0000</link><description>特鲁多发表此番言论之前，西奈山医院外发生了亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动，该医院由当地犹太社区创办，抗议者一边高呼“起义万岁”一边封锁交通。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 00:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/canadian-pm-denounces-reprehensible-protest-targeting-jewish-hospital-in-toronto/0000018d-a4f0-d42f-adcd-eff07cff0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日四天后，以色列发布了哈马斯头目辛瓦尔在加沙隧道的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-video-of-hamas-chief-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel-four-days-after-october-7/0000018d-a474-d400-a7cd-fff795410000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里告诉记者，这段视频是在安装在汗尤尼斯下方数十米的隧道中的安全摄像头中发现的，该视频是在过去几天拍摄的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 22:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-video-of-hamas-chief-sinwar-in-gaza-tunnel-four-days-after-october-7/0000018d-a474-d400-a7cd-fff795410000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 130 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-130/0000018d-a388-d8e9-a3bf-f3a8285e0000</link><description>摩萨德负责人、辛瓦尔在开罗与卡塔尔、埃及调解人进行停火/人质释放谈判的副手 ■ 南非就以色列即将在拉法实施的军事行动与国际法院接洽 ■ 法国表示将对袭击西方巴勒斯坦平民的 28 名定居者实施制裁银行 ■ 真主党的纳斯鲁拉表示，他的组织“致力于与以色列作战，直到以色列消失为止” ■ 以下是战争 130 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 18:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-130/0000018d-a388-d8e9-a3bf-f3a8285e0000</guid></item><item><title>法国与美国和英国一起制裁 28 名“极端主义”以色列约旦河西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/joining-the-u-s-and-u-k-france-sanctions-28-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018d-a311-d42f-adcd-ebf1ff310000</link><description>法国外交部还呼吁在更广泛的欧洲范围内实施类似的制裁。极右翼议员 Tzvi Succot：“不民主的程序，完全是根据极左组织的一时兴起而进行的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 17:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">ht